Package: picam-recorder
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libavformat-dev, libavcodec-dev, libavutil-dev
Description: RTSP stream recorder with pre/post buffer
 Records H.264 RTSP streams to MP4 files with configurable pre-roll
 and post-roll buffers. Controlled via a TCP plain-text protocol.
 Writes an MP4 and CSV metadata sidecar per recording.
